Heat oil in 12-inch nonstick skillet over medium heat. Add garlic, gingerroot, onion and bell pepper. Cook for 5 to 10 minutes, stirring occasionally, or until vegetables are tender. Add chicken. Cook for 3 minutes, stirring frequently, or until lightly browned. Pour in chicken broth and scrape up browned bits. Add apricots, apricot fruit spread, cumin, salt, pepper and cayenne pepper. Reduce heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes. Stir in Wacky Mac and simmer 5 minutes longer to heat through.